{"tid":1024943,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"星夢三女爭做一姐　天生命苦勁慘！","createTime":"2019-02-17T03:18:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-17T17:46:17.000Z","uid":27064,"like":9,"dislike":121,"uniUserReply":51,"replies":[{"pid":"ef0fa809813f57f59f83c58ec5bda9de2c966b56","tid":1024943,"uid":27064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T03:18:44.000Z","msg":"菊梓喬首奪「最受歡迎女歌星」，榮升「星夢一姐」，卻被網友質疑地位，指同公司還有吳若希及連詩雅，更發起「一人一票投選星夢一姐」選舉，以「菊姐」代表菊梓喬、「ABC連詩雅」代表連詩雅及以「吳大師姐」代表吳若希。滿以為菊梓喬命途坎坷，但原來吳若希及連詩雅亦有艱苦童年，三位背景十分相似！<br />\n<br />\n菊梓喬<br />\n自小父母離異，父母更在她13歲時遺棄她與妹妹，當時她頓失依靠，基本生活都成問題，更要擔起照顧妹妹的責任。她於中學年代亦被同學排擠及欺凌，最後索性輟學到社會工作，先後做過倉務員、美容院學徒、洗頭妹及洗碗妹等，努力工作供養妹妹讀書，更因收入不高，要一個即食麵分兩日食，更自爆患上罕見「多齒症」，醫生坦言沒有根治方法，非常悽慘！<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190217/photo/bkn-20190217032025228-0217_00862_001_04b.jpg?20190217082451\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190217%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190217032025228-0217_00862_001_04b.jpg%3F20190217082451&h=3787520e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n吳若希<br />\n在福建出世的吳若希，家境富裕，但童年時因爸爸生意問題而家道中落，最終父母離異。她10歲時跟隨母親來港生活，與公公、婆婆及姨姨在公屋居住。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190217/photo/bkn-20190217000013646-0217_00862_001_04p.jpg?20190217000422\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190217%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190217000013646-0217_00862_001_04p.jpg%3F20190217000422&h=69ef7218&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n連詩雅<br />\n自小家住九龍塘豪宅及就讀國際學校的連詩雅，原本生活無憂，但有傳父親生意失敗兼父母離婚，為慳錢要搬到劏房居住，並擔起養家責任。初出道時，她曾問公司借錢生活，並試過一日三餐食麵包充飢。<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/hbppjaq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fhbppjaq.jpg&h=7c6352d5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"361854cb6820628f57b98d0a0bee750688c71a35","tid":1024943,"uid":20725,"like":331,"dislike":2,"score":329,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T03:22:43.000Z","msg":"都係雞 仲有一個特別小氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3464e410added1782dfdb028f77530078b42e68e","tid":1024943,"uid":20291,"like":257,"dislike":1,"score":256,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T03:22:53.000Z","msg":"菊xx個張相，完美表演當年mk妹年代既感覺"},{"pid":"f4258463b404f127a99445168b81bca3f74a588f","tid":1024943,"uid":9193,"like":154,"dislike":2,"score":152,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T03:23:46.000Z","msg":"她10歲時跟隨母親來港生活<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85930386381d9adbca3ced688c03d6a63251a12a","tid":1024943,"uid":7699,"like":48,"dislike":6,"score":42,"quote":{"pid":"3464e410added1782dfdb028f77530078b42e68e","tid":1024943,"uid":20291,"like":257,"dislike":1,"score":256,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T03:22:53.000Z","msg":"菊xx個張相，完美表演當年mk妹年代既感覺"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T03:24:43.000Z","msg":"好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f46defa18dc3be783421788ee38396dda0639f41","tid":1024943,"uid":27064,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T03:25:04.000Z","msg":"連登仔捧邊個多啲?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"567c3d845f5e3e0fc888e45bc5104eb33952bcc0","tid":1024943,"uid":9193,"like":44,"dislike":1,"score":43,"quote":{"pid":"f46defa18dc3be783421788ee38396dda0639f41","tid":1024943,"uid":27064,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T03:25:04.000Z","msg":"連登仔捧邊個多啲?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T03:25:46.000Z","msg":"逢紅必反 全部都唔捧"},{"pid":"167ca5d023b1cfed7fdb225d967307397717446a","tid":1024943,"uid":57329,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,